snippet.textDisplay: I actually have adhd I was diagnosed with it in 4th grade so they started giving me medicine I took like 4 different kinds some of them made me sick I got headaches and stomach some of them made me concentrate even less than I did before I took the medication so I missed out on a lot of school because I was constantly feeling bad so then in 6th I told my mom she believed me because I had told her many times before so she called the doctor and they said they only had a appointment available in a couple of weeks and I couldn't handle it any more so I just stopped taking the medication I really felt like some sort of test subject and to anyone saying that this is made up its not I don't have any proof but it happened to me I and just wanted to share it on this song because it is a pretty accurate representation of what life felt like those 2 years.
